  <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> November 2025</p>

  <p>Welcome to <strong>Black And Pink 4K Wallpapers</strong>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>App Information:</strong> We collect basic application data (package name, version number, and developer info) to ensure the app works properly and remains compatible with all devices.</li>
    <li><strong>Wi-Fi Status:</strong> The app may check your Wi-Fi connection status to optimize the download of wallpapers and improve performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Network Type:</strong> We may collect your current network type (Wi-Fi, 4G, 5G, etc.) to adjust image quality and app behavior.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Advertising and Marketing</h2>
  <p>This app may display third-party ads (such as Google AdMob). These partners may use cookies or similar technologies to show personalized ads. No personal data like your name, phone number, or address is collected by this app.</p>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell or share your personal data. Limited technical information may be processed by third-party advertising services for analytics and ad delivery purposes.</p>

  <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
